Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:58.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可不好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:13.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:15.29,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它們就這麼喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:16.68,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為我是暗黑騎士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.33,0:01:20.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:25.02,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}黑暗啊 惡德之王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.86,0:01:28.59,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}召喚惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:35.38,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}膽小鬼藍德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.48,0:01:36.78,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}膽小鬼毛毛蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:38.51,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}毛毛蟲毛毛蟲毛毛蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:41.36,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}毛毛蟲毛毛蟲毛毛蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:43.61,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}毛毛蟲毛毛蟲毛毛蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.61,0:01:46.25,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}毛毛蟲毛毛蟲毛毛蟲...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:49.63,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行不行不行不行
