Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:15.79,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}治癒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:23.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是夢兒最後一支箭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:29.53,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家往這邊 夢兒也過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能跑嗎 藍德
